history.content: 99%. It's not uncommon for undeclared/non-CS majors to get into 170. Up until funding cuts that has a reputation of letting everyone in.

Is there any chance that I would get into the class at the time when I officially get declared, which would be 2-3 weeks after the declaration deadline (December 30th)?

Would you recommend enrolling into 170 or should I wait to get declared and then enroll into this class?

Thanks in advance
